      • nextTraverser

        public Traverser.Admin<E> nextTraverser()
        Description copied from class: AbstractRemoteTraversal
        Note that internally AbstractRemoteTraversal.nextTraverser() is called from within a loop (specifically in AbstractStep.next() that breaks properly when a NoSuchElementException is thrown. In other words the "results" should be iterated to force that failure.
